List the requirements needed to add a third activity that could be used to display flash cards. 
1- create the string arrays for the words and definitions. 
2- Add a new activity called flash cards. 
3- add a button to the main activity that will launch the flash cards activity. 
4- design the flash card activity XML with a textview that will switch between word and definition. Add to buttons (flip card , next )
5- add function code to the java file that will handle the two button clicks. 
